{
    "title": "O Noivo Vem",
    "artist": "Jonathan Silva",
    "lyricsHtml": "\n[Intro] <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#m\">G#m</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M\">D#M</span>  <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M7\">D#M7</span>\n\n    <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">É tempo de nos santificar , para na quele dia o noivo encontrar juntos</span>\n              <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M7\">D#M7</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Junto com os anjos eu vou adorar , para todo sempre seu nome plocamar</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>                                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>                                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">E a sua face quero contemplar , e juntos com os anjos vamos declarar  , santo , santo</span>\n       <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Santo é o senhoor </span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Santo , ele e santo , santo , santo , santo é o senhoor</span>\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Santo , ele e santo , santo , santo , santo é o senhoor</span>\n\n<span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>                 <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>                <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>                             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Aviva-nos , aviva a sua igreja , para que possamos estar revestido ao teu grande encontro</span>\n      <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>                   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">Triunfal , mais uma vez , jesus venceu o maau</span>\n <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"C#M\">C#M</span>           <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>             <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"D#M9\">D#M9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O noivo vem , o nivo vem , o noivem , o noivo vem</span>\n\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O noivo vem melhor se preparar , o noivo vem aqui nao vou ficar , o noivo vem é tempo de adorar</span>\n   <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span>                               <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span>                                     <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O noivo vem melhor se preparar , o noivo vem aqui nao vou ficar , o noivo vem é tempo de adorar</span>\n\n         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#7\">F#7</span>                                         <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"G#M\">G#M</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"E\">E</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B\">B</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"F#\">F#</span> <span class=\"chord\" data-chord=\"B9\">B9</span>\n<span class=\"lyric-line\">O noivo vem , corra enquanto a tempo para aqui nao ficaa</span>\n",
